---
alt: Studio auth flow sequence
---
sequenceDiagram
    accTitle: Studio Authentication Flow
    accDescr: Sequence of calls for admin login and studio session activation

    actor Admin
    participant AdminPage as /admin page
    participant LoginAPI as POST /api/__studio/auth/login
    participant StatusAPI as GET /api/__studio/auth/status
    participant RateLimiter as In-Memory Rate Limiter
    participant Session as studio-session cookie
    participant StudioMiddleware as studio-auth middleware
    participant StudioUI as Nuxt Studio Overlay

    Admin->>AdminPage: Navigate to /admin
    Admin->>LoginAPI: POST {username, password}
    LoginAPI->>RateLimiter: checkRateLimit(ip)
    alt Too many attempts
        RateLimiter-->>LoginAPI: 429 Too Many Requests
        LoginAPI-->>Admin: Error response
    else Credentials valid
        LoginAPI->>Session: Set studio-session cookie
        LoginAPI-->>AdminPage: 200 OK
        AdminPage->>Admin: Redirect to /
    else Credentials invalid
        LoginAPI->>RateLimiter: recordFailedAttempt(ip)
        LoginAPI-->>Admin: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over Admin,StudioUI: On any studio-auth protected page
    Admin->>StudioMiddleware: Route navigation
    StudioMiddleware->>StatusAPI: GET /api/__studio/auth/status
    StatusAPI->>Session: Read session.data.user
    alt Authenticated
        StatusAPI-->>StudioMiddleware: {authenticated: true}
        StudioMiddleware-->>StudioUI: Allow - overlay activates
    else Not authenticated
        StatusAPI-->>StudioMiddleware: {authenticated: false}
        StudioMiddleware-->>Admin: Redirect to /admin
    end
